Synopsis: Takes a changelog in Keep a Changelog 1.0.0 format and parses the data into a PowerShell object.
Description: Takes a changelog in Keep a Changelog 1.0.0 format and parses the data into a PowerShell object.
Inputs: This cmdlet does not accept pipeline input.
Outputs: This cmdlet outputs a PSCustomObject containing the changelog data.

Examples.Title: EXAMPLE 1
Examples.Code:
Get-ChangelogData
Returns an object containing Header, Unreleased, Released, Footer, and LastVersion properties.
